## ⚙️ CUSTOMIZATION REQUIRED

**Before Using This Workflow:**

1. **Google Sheets CRM:** Update document ID to your CRM
2. **Template Document:** Point to your proposal template
3. **Gmail Settings:** Configure sender email
4. **OpenRouter API:** Add your API credentials
5. **Fathom Webhook:** Configure webhook secret

**Template Placeholders:**
Ensure your Google Doc template contains these placeholders:
- {{text}}, {{description}}, {{companyname}}
- {{problem}}, {{projectaim}}, {{projectgoal}}
- {{firstsolutionheading}}, {{secondsolutionheading}}, {{thirdsolutionheading}}
- {{phase1}}, {{phase2}}, {{phase3}}, {{phase4}}
- {{cost1}}, {{cost2}}, {{firstdeadline}}, {{seconddeadline}}

